query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS emailTracking (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  emailQueueId INT NOT NULL,
  leadId INT NOT NULL,
  trackingId VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL UNIQUE,
  opened BOOLEAN DEFAULT FALSE NOT NULL,
  openedAt TIMESTAMP NULL,
  openCount INT DEFAULT 0 NOT NULL,
  clicked BOOLEAN DEFAULT FALSE NOT NULL,
  clickedAt TIMESTAMP NULL,
  clickCount INT DEFAULT 0 NOT NULL,
  userAgent TEXT,
  ipAddress VARCHAR(45),
  createdAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS emailBlacklist (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  email VARCHAR(320) NOT NULL UNIQUE,
  reason TEXT,
  unsubscribedAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  createdAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
);
